        "range": null,
        "overview": {
          "base": "You may create 1 custom \"rotator\" @L[Category:Spells]{spells} using @L[Core:Elder Sorcery]{Elder Sorcery} words that you know using whatever @L[Core:Elder Sorcery]{Elder Sorcery} creation rules are dictated to you by your @L[Core:GM]{GM}. As with other rotators, this spell is not always available to you. You have to \"rotate\" into having it prepared. This spell may have a maximum number of words equal to your @L[Core:Leveling Up]{level}. Your @L[Core:GM]{GM} may allow you to \"improvise\" @L[Category:Spells]{spells} as well, using whatever rules they wish.",
          "proficient": "You may now create 2 × (@L[Category:Mage classes]{MR} - 1) custom \"rotator\" @L[Category:Spells]{spells} where @L[Category:Mage classes]{MR} is the number of @L[Core:Leveling Up]{ranks} you have in @L[Category:Mage classes]{mage classes}.",
          "fluent": "In addition to the spells that you crate, you can learn @L[Core:Proficiency Bonus]{P} additional spells from other @L[Core:Elder Sorcery]{Elder Sorcery} users. See @L[Core:Elder Sorcery]{Elder Sorcery} for more information."
